description: Always bump service worker cache version after PWA asset changes
alwaysApply: true
---

# PWA cache bump rule

- If you edit PWA-served assets (`public/index.html`, `public/sw.js`, manifest, icons, CSS, JS), you must increment `CACHE` in `public/sw.js`.
- Keep the version monotonic (`v41` -> `v42` -> `v43`).
- Mention the cache bump explicitly in your final summary so it is visible in review.
